# ✋ Gesture Controlled Desktop System

A real-time computer vision project that allows controlling a computer using hand gestures without touching the keyboard or mouse.

---

## 🚀 Features

- 🎯 Real-time hand tracking using MediaPipe  
- ✋ Finger counting and gesture recognition  
- 🔊 Volume control  
- 🔇 Mute / Unmute  
- 🌐 Open applications (YouTube)  
- 🔒 Lock system  
- 🖥 Interactive UI  

---

## 🛠 Tech Stack

- Python  
- OpenCV  
- MediaPipe  
- PyAutoGUI  
- Tkinter  

---

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
pip install opencv-python mediapipe pyautogui pillow
python app_ui.py
